  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Forum rooms</strong> sleep two people and are around 15m², with views across the resort's Forum. Classic rooms are also available for sole occupancy, please give our Reservations team a call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Club rooms</strong> sleep two people and are around 25m², with panoramic mountain views and a balcony. An additional bed is available for children between 4 and 12 years old, on request. Club rooms are also available for sole occupancy, please give our Reservations team a call to book.</p>
<p>Club rooms can fit a cot. A Baby kit including a cot and a baby bath is available locally with a charge of €15 per day.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>Interconnecting rooms are available on request.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>All rooms have a unique mural</li>
<li>Mountain views</li>
<li>Twin or double beds (please specify preference when booking)</li>
<li>Satellite TV</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Tea and coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Telephone</li>
<li>Radio</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Toiletries</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Bath with shower head attachment or shower room</li>
<li>Daily house keeping is included</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
